FT  02 APR 93 / UK Company News: Lightship in talks over balance sheet
Lightship, the financial services company, said yesterday that it was in
advanced talks concerning the strengthening of its balance sheet.
It was expected that these discussions would be completed by the end of May,
at which time its preliminary and interim results would be released.
The results for the year to end-June 1992 were expected to be announced by
the end of last month. The company's shares were suspended at its own
request in January.
